summary:
üëã Hi, I'm Caro Quezada, a passionate omnichannel and digital expert in the pharma industry since 2014. Currently part of the Global Omnichannel operation Lead team at Gr√ºnenthal, I'm driven by the power of seamless strategies that transcend boundaries within our cluster. Previously, as Head Multichannel Manager at Gr√ºnenthal Chile üá®üá±, I optimized digital platforms for increased sales impact and added value to internal and external stakeholders. Earlier, during my 5-year tenure at Pfizer, I served as Digital Experience Lead (and other positions), elevating coverage, frequency, and conversion rates to maximize ROI. My mission is to lead the charge in revolutionizing the pharma industry with cutting-edge technology, crafting next-level patient-centric solutions that truly make a difference! üöÄ Let's team up and drive our industry forward, harnessing the power of CX (Customer Experience), mastering the art of omnichannel magic, and staying ahead of the innovation game! üåü Together, we'll create a healthcare experience like no other, putting patients at the heart of it all! ü§ù
